ass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該講緊幫公司賺到百五萬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印象中 地產公司係會收樓價1%作為佣金<br />\n（有錯請指正）<br />\n<br />\n即600萬樓價<br />\n會收6萬為 服務費<br />\n至於6萬 經紀 同 公司 就按比例分拆<br />\n比例應該都係睇grade"},{"pid":"5771495b3c29dff4561a8e40759e7282065e32c8","tid":303019,"uid":5890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為咗儲錢上車, 連棚牙都唔去箍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n箍佐應該無咁靚"},{"pid":"798941fc55078da8bb1f61fb252e021245596bb7","tid":303019,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>為咗儲錢上車, 連棚牙都唔去箍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n箍佐應該無咁靚</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有D 人好鐘意老虎爆牙仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1843b0bb88a45f2c8ff5818484ff38d12a6e38f","tid":303019,"uid":52188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>為咗儲錢上車, 連棚牙都唔去箍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n箍佐應該無咁靚</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有D 人好鐘意老虎爆牙仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爆牙根本係樣衰"},{"pid":"a0a5b24bb37d4b42c71865cc9943f226e2a3b3e9","tid":303019,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:46:27.000Z","msg":"唔打開嘴又幾正"},{"pid":"d17746101e9f4d38bf2e79c775f12dae6b2f3de5","tid":303019,"uid":10929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"要做工作狂先上到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係上車後都要keep住博殺去供"},{"pid":"d4f276cbc0a4f852ce626cda4fdfd59d42d993fe","tid":303019,"uid":55142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:00:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過去半年跑數150萬元？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該講緊幫公司賺到百五萬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印象中 地產公司係會收樓價1%作為佣金<br />\n（有錯請指正）<br />\n<br />\n即600萬樓價<br />\n會收6萬為 服務費<br />\n至於6萬 經紀 同 公司 就按比例分拆<br />\n比例應該都係睇grade</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係睇每個發展商<br />\n唔同樓盤都唔同佣 (一手樓計)<br />\n一般都係3隻-5隻佣  (樓價3-5%)<br />\n比得5隻佣既盤都叫做好闊佬<br />\n通常係偽豪宅個類<br />\n<br />\n呢一筆錢首先要比公司 (3-5成左右)<br />\n之後又要比陀地 <br />\n又再分比你上司 (區頭個d)<br />\n實際落場肉博既aa 係得返3成左右<br />\n佣通常係成交後半年以後先出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而上面大粒個d (區頭或以上)<br />\n唔可以自己搵客同sell客<br />\n就算你有客都要介紹比你d 細既<br />\n等佢地幫你做 你再抽佢地既一部分佣<br />\n所以你d細既搵得愈多 你就抽得愈多<br />\n<br />\n不過有好多人如果有客 把口又ok<br />\n寧願自己一直做細 唔會升上去<br />\n睇你自己點揀<br />\n<br />\n利申: 發展商入面做"},{"pid":"5b643c29ab7d19576b2e724fff0871361c467c75","tid":303019,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:26:22.000Z","msg":"有ball嗎？"},{"pid":"572a925c915303f0b67b805742ad8b47ea6cd1bb","tid":303019,"uid":4896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"高級客戶董事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1dca2476ad566e2447cb2e88704a925800a53b","tid":303019,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要做工作狂先上到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係上車後都要keep住博殺去供</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n王維基真係無講錯，年輕人敢片又怕辛苦又唔肯捱，未ready , 淨係識怨政府！"},{"pid":"dbd7e931d87f52dcf427ba20a5169e4244f05e89","tid":303019,"uid":59602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"留名等流出"}]}